# This file defines teams or individuals responsible for code review
# for different parts of the codebase.
#
# Format:
#   pattern @username
#   pattern @team
#
# Patterns are relative to the repository root
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-codeowners

